import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom'

function ReactRouter() {
    return (
        <Router >
            <Routes>
                <Route />
                <Route />
                <Route />
            </Routes>
        </Router>
    )
}

export default ReactRouter
